Phn tch tc dng cc loi thuc chng trm cm

Thnh vin:

  • 23C24004 - L Nht Nam
  • 23C24005 - Phm Tha Tiu Thnh

Ng cnh vn : D liu c cho trong tp tin cha thng tin v mt th nghim v tc dng ph ca cc loi thuc chng trm cm i vi tr nh ca ngi tham gia th nghim, c nh gi thng qua thi gian hon thnh mt bi kim tra tr nh. Ngi tham gia th nghim s c s dng mt trong ba loi thuc khc nhau, vi 3 hm lng khc nhau v s tip xc vi cc k c vui hoc bun trong vng 10 pht trc khi tin hnh kim tra. Thi gian hon thnh bi kim tra ca ngi tham gia s c ghi nhn trc v sau khi kt thc th nghim nh gi hiu qu ca tng loi thuc cng nh hm lng thuc khc nhau. (Nhng ngi ny u trn 25 tui nhm m bo thu trn pht trin hon thin, ni m nhn chc nng nhn thc v gi li k c). D liu c thu thp bi ng Almohalwas ti UCLA bao gm 198 quan trc vi 9 bin.

Dn nhp

Cc loi thuc benzodiazepin cho thy c tc dng ph v tc ng tch cc ca tim nng lu di gia cc t bo i vi vic thu hi tr nh v cc mi lin h bit. Bng cch phn bit cc tc dng ph lu di ca Alprazolam (di hn) v Triazolam (ngn hn), bnh nhn c th c chn on tt hn gim thiu bt k tn thng no i vi kh nng siu nhn thc (metacognition) v thu hi tr nh ca no. Nghin cu su hn cng ch ra rng ch cn nh li nhng k c c th c lin quan n cm xc mnh m s khin nhng cm xc c hin thc ha thi im hin ti v nh hng n nhng suy ngh trong tng lai trong mt khong thi gian ngn (khong 10 pht). S hin din ca cm xc vui v cm xc bun c quan tm v c bit l c nh hng ng k n vic thu hi tr nh, t t ra cu hi, nhng nh hng no n hiu sut thu hi tr nh ca cc thuc benzodiazepin sau khi c bt u bng k c vui hay bun? Nghin cu lm sng ny s cho thy liu tm trng ca k c h tr hoc cn tr vic nh li tr nh c c lp vi cc yu t khc hay khng, nu hiu qu ca thuc benzodiazepin khng ch ph thuc vo kh nng chu ng ca ngi tham gia m cn c tm trng ca h, v cui cng l kh nng tng cng hoc lm gim hiu sut nh li tr nh khi c kt hp cng nhau vt ra ngoi phn ng bit vi vic s dng thuc benzodiazepin hoc k c lin quan n tm trng ca ring bnh nhn.

Cc thng tin v b d liu

  • D liu cha thng tin v mt th nghim v tc dng ph ca cc loi thuc chng trm cm i vi tr nh ca ngi tham gia th nghim, c nh gi thng qua thi gian hon thnh mt bi kim tra tr nh. Ngi tham gia th nghim s c s dng mt trong ba loi thuc khc nhau, vi 3 hm lng khc nhau v s tip xc vi cc k c vui hoc bun trong vng 10 pht trc khi tin hnh kim tra. Thi gian hon thnh bi kim tra ca ngi tham gia s c ghi nhn trc v sau khi kt thc th nghim nh gi hiu qu ca tng loi thuc cng nh hm lng thuc khc nhau. (Nhng ngi ny u trn 25 tui nhm m bo thu trn pht trin hon thin, ni m nhn chc nng nhn thc v gi li k c). D liu c thu thp bi ng Almohalwas ti UCLA bao gm 198 quan trc vi 9 bin sau:

    • first-name: tn ca ngi tham gia th nghim
    • last-name: h ca ngi tham gia th nghim
    • Age: tui (nm) ca ngi tham gia th nghim
    • HappySadgroup: loi k c c tip xc trc khi kim tra (H: vui, S: bun)
    • Dosage: Mc hm lng thuc s dng (1: thp, 2: trung bnh, 3: cao)
    • Drug: Loi thuc s dng (A: , Alprazolam, T: Triazolam, S: Placebo)
    • Mem-Score-Before: Thi gian (giy) cn hon thnh bi kim tra trc khi tip xc vi thuc cha trm cm
    • Mem-Score-After: Thi gian (giy) cn hon thnh bi kim tra sau khi tip xc vi thuc cha trm cm
    • Diff: Chnh lch gia thi gian (giy) hon thnh bi kim tra trc v sau khi s dng thuc.

  • D liu c tt c 198 quan trc

Mt s nhn xt v b d liu nh sau

  • Cc bin first-name v last-name cha thng tin v tn ca ngi kho st (kiu d liu character), v mt thng k bin ny khng c ngha nn s c loi b khi d liu khi kho st.
  • Cc bin HappySadgroup, Dosage v Drug c th hin di dng catogory (nhm) v th s c asFactor trc khi kho st.
  • Cc bin Mem-Score-Before, Mem-Score-After, v Diff c th hin di dng kiu d liu numeric, tuy nhin, y ta c Diff = Mem-Score-Before - Mem-Score-After (a cng tuyn), v vy ta ch cn kho st bin ph thuc Diff, cc bin cn li s loi b ra khi d liu trc khi kho st.
  • age kiu d liu int, cha thng tin v tui ca ngi kho st, dao ng t 24 tui n 83 tui. Thay v kho st trn tng nhm tui ring bit (rt nhiu), ta s tin hnh chia thnh 2 nhm chnh l nhm tui < 50 v nhm cn li.

Nhn xt:

  • Liu lng thp:
    • Trung v Diff gn bng 0, vi phm vi nh.
    • Hu ht cc im d liu tp trung xung quanh trung v, vi mt vi ngoi l.
  • Liu lng trung bnh:
    • Trung v Diff vn gn bng 0, nhng phm vi d liu ln hn mt cht so vi liu lng thp.
    • C s phn b rng hn ca cc im, cho thy s bin i nhiu hn trong cc phn ng.
  • Liu lng cao:
    • Trung v Diff cao hn so vi cc nhm khc, gi rng liu lng thuc ny c tc dng ln hn.
    • C s bin i ln, vi mt s im nm kh cao hoc thp so vi trung v.
    • IQR ln hn v s hin din ca cc ngoi l cho thy mt phm vi rng ca cc phn ng i vi liu lng cao.

Kt lun

  • Biu gi rng liu lng cao hn c th c tc ng ng k hn n thi gian hon thnh bi kim tra tr nh, c ch ra bi trung v cao hn v s bin i ln hn trong Diff.
  • Liu lng thp v trung bnh cho thy s thay i nh hn v t bin i hn, vi nhiu ngi tham gia c t hoc khng thay i trong thi gian hon thnh.
  • S phn b rng hn v trung v cao hn trong nhm liu lng cao c th cho thy rng mc d mt s ngi tham gia c li ch ng k, nhng ngi khc c th gp tc dng ph, dn n phn ng khng tt.

BIU BN TRI

Biu bn tri biu din s tng tc gia Dosage v Drug da trn gi tr trung bnh iu chnh ca Diff.

  1. th trn cng bn tri (Dosage theo Drug):

    • Cho thy s thay i ca Diff theo liu lng (Dosage) cho tng loi thuc (Drug).
    • i vi tt c cc loi thuc, Diff tng dn khi tng liu lng t 1 n 3.

  2. th di cng bn tri (Drug theo Dosage):

  • Cho thy s thay i ca Diff theo loi thuc (Drug) cho tng liu lng (Dosage).
  • Khi liu lng l 1: s khc bit gia cc loi thuc l tng i nh. Trong loi S cho hiu qu cao nht, A v T cho kt qu t hn trc khi s dng (mean < 0).
  • Khi liu l 2: C s thay i r rt cc loi thuc: Loi S cho kt qu t hn so vi trc khi dng thuc, loi T c hiu qu khng ng k, loi A cho thy hiu qu vt bt.
  • Khi liu lng l 3: S khc bit gia cc loi thuc tr nn r rt hn, vi Thuc A cho kt qu tt nht so vi 3 loi v c 3 liu lng, trong khi 2 loi cn li cho kt qu t hn trc khi dng.

BIU BN PHI

Biu bn phi biu din s tng tc gia Drug v Dosage da trn gi tr trung bnh iu chnh ca Diff.

  1. th trn cng bn phi (Drug theo Dosage):

    • Tng t nh th di cng bn tri ca biu bn tri, nhng theo chiu ngc li. Cho thy s thay i ca Diff theo loi thuc cho tng liu lng.
    • i vi thuc A: Cho kt qu tt liu lng cao v trung bnh, liu lng thp khng c s thay i
    • i vi thuc T: Khng c s khc bit gia cc liu lng v hiu qu sau v trc khi sng dng (Thm ch gim (t))
    • i vi thuc S: Ging T

  2. th di cng bn phi (Dosage theo Drug):

    • Tng t nh th trn cng bn tri ca biu bn tri, nhng theo chiu ngc li.
    • Cho thy s thay i ca Diff theo liu lng cho tng loi thuc.
    • C bn cc thuc cho kt qu tt nht theo th t l l A > S > T.

NHN XT

  • C liu lng v loi thuc u c nh hng ng k n Diff.
  • C s tng tc ng k gia liu lng v loi thuc, ngha l hiu qu ca liu lng khc nhau ph thuc vo loi thuc c s dng.
  • Biu cho thy r rng rng Thuc A (Alprazolam) c nh hng ln nht khi liu lng tng, trong khi S c nh hng t nht.

    • Nhm T-S c p-value > 0.05 nn khng bc b H0, vy nhm ny c gi tr trung bnh bng nhau.
    • Cc nhm cn li p-value u c gi tr nh hn 0.05 ( tin cy 95%) nn ta c c s bc b H0. Vy r rng gia cc nhm ny c gi tr trung bnh l khc nhau. Ngha l cc nhm thuc khc nhau th cho thy mc nh hng n bnh nhn khc nhau. r hn, ta tin hnh kim nh Tukey's
  • Nhn vo kt qu v hnh v ta cng thy ngay gia nhm S-A v T-A c mc hiu qu trung bnh khc nhau, T-S c mc hiu qu trung bnh nh nhau ( th ct im 0)

Xy dng v kim nh m hnh cng (Additive model)

Gm cc bc sau:

  • Xy dng m hnh vi cc bin
  • Kim nh m hnh

# Kho st ngoi lai theo bin diff
diff_data = processed_islander["Diff"]
outliers_index = list()
extreme_outliers_index = list()

for (i in 1:ncol(diff_data)) {
  # Tnh ton Q1, Q3 v IQR
  Q1 = quantile(diff_data[, i], 0.25, na.rm = TRUE)
  Q3 = quantile(diff_data[, i], 0.75, na.rm = TRUE)
  IQR = Q3 - Q1

  # Xc nh ngoi lai
  outliers_index_i = diff_data[, i] < (Q1 - 1.5 * IQR) | diff_data[, i] > (Q3 + 1.5 * IQR)
  # outliers_i = diff_data[diff_data[, i] < (Q1 - 1.5 * IQR) | diff_data[, i] > (Q3 + 1.5 * IQR), i]

  # Lu tr ngoi lai
  field_name = names(diff_data)[i]
  outliers_index[[field_name]] = which(outliers_index_i)

  # Xc nh cc ngoi lai
  extreme_outliers_index_i = diff_data[, i] < (Q1 - 3 * IQR) | diff_data[, i] > (Q3 + 3 * IQR)
  extreme_outliers_index[[field_name]] = which(extreme_outliers_index_i)
}
# In kt qu theo tng bin ra mn hnh
for (i in 1:ncol(diff_data)) {
  print(paste("Bin:", names(diff_data)[i]))
  print(paste("S ngoi lai:", length(outliers_index[[names(diff_data)[i]]])))
  print(paste("S cc ngoi lai:", length(extreme_outliers_index[[names(diff_data)[i]]])))
}

# Tm tng s quan trc ngoi lai v cc ngoi lai thc s
outliers = c()
extreme_outliners = c()
for (i in 1:ncol(diff_data)){
    outliers = c(outliers, outliers_index[[names(diff_data)[i]]])
    extreme_outliners = c(extreme_outliners, extreme_outliers_index[[names(diff_data)[i]]])
}

outliers = unique(outliers)
extreme_outliners = unique(extreme_outliners)
print(paste("Tng s ngoi lai:", length(outliers)))
print(paste("Tng s cc ngoi lai:", length(extreme_outliners)))

BIU BN TRI

Biu bn tri biu din s tng tc gia Dosage v Drug da trn gi tr trung bnh iu chnh ca Diff.

  1. th trn cng bn tri (Dosage theo Drug):

    • Cho thy s thay i ca Diff theo liu lng (Dosage) cho tng loi thuc (Drug).
    • i vi tt c cc loi thuc, Diff tng dn khi tng liu lng t 1 n 3.

  2. th di cng bn tri (Drug theo Dosage):

  • Cho thy s thay i ca Diff theo loi thuc (Drug) cho tng liu lng (Dosage).
  • Khi liu lng l 1: s khc bit gia cc loi thuc l tng i nh. Trong loi S cho hiu qu cao nht, A v T cho kt qu t hn trc khi s dng (mean < 0).
  • Khi liu l 2: C s thay i r rt cc loi thuc: Loi S cho kt qu t hn so vi trc khi dng thuc, loi T c hiu qu khng ng k, loi A cho thy hiu qu vt bt.
  • Khi liu lng l 3: S khc bit gia cc loi thuc tr nn r rt hn, vi Thuc A cho kt qu tt nht so vi 3 loi v c 3 liu lng, trong khi 2 loi cn li cho kt qu t hn trc khi dng.

BIU BN PHI

Biu bn phi biu din s tng tc gia Drug v Dosage da trn gi tr trung bnh iu chnh ca Diff.

  1. th trn cng bn phi (Drug theo Dosage):

    • Tng t nh th di cng bn tri ca biu bn tri, nhng theo chiu ngc li. Cho thy s thay i ca Diff theo loi thuc cho tng liu lng.
    • i vi thuc A: Cho kt qu tt liu lng cao v trung bnh, liu lng thp khng c s thay i
    • i vi thuc T: Khng c s khc bit gia cc liu lng v hiu qu sau v trc khi sng dng (Thm ch gim (t))
    • i vi thuc S: Ging T

  2. th di cng bn phi (Dosage theo Drug):

    • Tng t nh th trn cng bn tri ca biu bn tri, nhng theo chiu ngc li.
    • Cho thy s thay i ca Diff theo liu lng cho tng loi thuc.
    • C bn cc thuc cho kt qu tt nht theo th t l l A > S > T.

NHN XT

  • C liu lng v loi thuc u c nh hng ng k n Diff.
  • C s tng tc ng k gia liu lng v loi thuc, ngha l hiu qu ca liu lng khc nhau ph thuc vo loi thuc c s dng.
  • Biu cho thy r rng rng Thuc A (Alprazolam) c nh hng ln nht khi liu lng tng, trong khi S c nh hng t nht.

  • Drug2:H s cho Drug2 l 0.9726. iu ny cho thy rng khi s dng loi thuc th hai, s khc bit trong thi gian hon thnh bi kim tra gim i 0.9726 giy so vi khng s dng thuc. Tuy nhin, h s ny khng c ngha thng k (p-value = 0.230799 > 0.05).

Kt lun: Nu xem bn thn loi thuc v liu thuc tng tc mt cch c lp, th sau y l khuyn ngh cho bc s: Nn s dng loi thuc 2 (thuc S) cho bnh nhn. Thc t th vic s dng thuc cn nh gi nhiu kha cnh (v d nh phn tch nh hng n cho thy tng tc mnh vi liu lng) V vy, cn phi cn thn cn nhc khi s dng thuc trnh em li hu qu khng mong mun ngoi tm kim sot.

Nh vy v tng th sao khi loi b cc im ngoi lai v cc ngoi lai, v vieeck thng k v phn tch ANOVA cho ra mt m hnh c cc yu t tha mn cc yu t kim nh v chun hn, trong TH khng chun nhng ch s so vi trc l tt hn
